body:
The first error usually happens when the ResNet weights are not found or the TensorFlow installation is faulty, see
https://github.com/DeepLabCut/DeepLabCut/issues/667
and https://github.com/DeepLabCut/DeepLabCut/issues/358

rename.to: Could not create cudnn handle: CUDNN_STATUS_ALLOC_FAILED
